The local government has also placed a great emphasis on innovation, employment and economic growth in the Geelong region.

As the Manager Residential Aged Care in the Aged Care Directorate, you will be located within the McKellar Centre, however you will be required to visit other Barwon Health locations specifically those within your directorate. Located at McKellar Centre (Nth Geelong) and In Grovedale, the four residential facilities total 397 beds.

About The Role

In this role as the Manager Residential Aged Care you will be accountable to the Co-Director for strategic and operational leadership of the residential aged care services and contributing to the achievement of the Directorate’s and Barwon Health’s Strategic Plan and objectives.

Duties Of This Significant And Challenging Role Includes
  • Development of service plans and Key Performance Indictors (KPI’s)
  • Manage staff operational issues within the Directorate
  • Oversee and manage quality aspects of care provision
  • Liaise with stakeholders and service providers to achieve successful working partnerships
  • Support the professional growth and development of facility staff
